  "detailed_description": "In Eternal Burden you play as William, a restless soul trying to go back in time to get rid of his burdens, symbolized by a metal ball chained to his body. Use the ball to your advantage to get over obstacles and to solve the physics based puzzles that block your path to liberation.<br><br>-Change the ball's size as you deem fit in order to overcome any obstacle<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744070/extras/0c10f12dca9e3cc4fc02ec619860f7b1.avif?t=1708696819\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744070/extras/43ab35af52e20a16aa91f04dc35b0de1.avif?t=1708696819\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>-Solve a unique set of physics based puzzles<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744070/extras/6eeffd6de32988af010efddd9f110582.avif?t=1708696819\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>-Use your brain to place the correct amount of weight on each scale in order to open the door<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744070/extras/c1a0cb07979e46bc123d3c24e2e2bbea.avif?t=1708696819\" width=616 height=346 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "In Eternal Burden you play as William, a restless soul trying to go back in time to get rid of his burdens, symbolized by a metal ball chained to his body. Use the ball to your advantage to get over obstacles and to solve the physics based puzzles that block your path to liberation.<br><br>-Change the ball's size as you deem fit in order to overcome any obstacle<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744070/extras/0c10f12dca9e3cc4fc02ec619860f7b1.avif?t=1708696819\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744070/extras/43ab35af52e20a16aa91f04dc35b0de1.avif?t=1708696819\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>-Solve a unique set of physics based puzzles<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744070/extras/6eeffd6de32988af010efddd9f110582.avif?t=1708696819\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>-Use your brain to place the correct amount of weight on each scale in order to open the door<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2744070/extras/c1a0cb07979e46bc123d3c24e2e2bbea.avif?t=1708696819\" width=616 height=346 /></span>",
